    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking a reliable, well-maintained car that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, with only minor road wear expected of a carefully driven vehicle. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is supple with minimal signs of use, and every electronic component\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with recent oil changes and a fresh set of high-performance tires. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and certain. Whether you are commuting or taking a long weekend road trip, this car offers a composed and confident ride. It comes with a full set of keys and a complete service history for your peace of mind.",
      "price": 36250.0,
